bassa is a local government area in the north of plateau state, nigeria, bordering kaduna and bauchi states. its headquarters are in the town of bassa at9°56′00″n 8°44′00″e﻿ / ﻿9.93333°n 8.73333°e. it has an area of 1,743 km² and a population of 186,859 at the 2006 census. the postal code of the area is 930.